 acquire the instruction, the content playback authorization determination unit switches from the content being displayed to the acquired content, and when the content playback authorization determination unit acquires a rejection instruction, the content playback authorization determination unit causes the display unit to continue display of the content being displayed.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>